Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,322号机严重受损
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.19,0:00:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紧急弹射！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,森少尉由于后冲力受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.91,0:00:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然把森给…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别过来！
