Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿法小队 准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.02,0:13:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涯！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作战开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,导弹接近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,截击！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葬仪社吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千万别漏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.17,0:13:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 集
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿法小队进行远距离攻击之后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.69,0:14:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能地将End Rave从敌阵引开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.53,0:14:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引开至预定的距离后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查理小队开始行动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对据点红 蓝 黄完成压制
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离预定距离还有7
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绫姐 我的孩子们就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
